  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  You are willing to take part in the study, including signing this form after carefully
             reading it.

          -  You are available for follow-up for a minimum of 24 months (2 years).

          -  You have no medical conditions that prevent you from having surgery.

          -  This is the primary (first) knee replacement for this knee

          -  You are fluent in English and are able to understand your responsibilities in this
             study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Active, local or systemic infection

          -  Fibromyalgia or other chronic pain syndrome

          -  Inability to follow the study requirements

          -  Had this knee replaced before

          -  Had a previous surgery on this knee that would interfere with the MIS approach
             (examples are femoral-femoral bypass, femoral-popliteal bypass, and quadricepsplasty)

          -  Body Mass Index (BMI) &gt; 35, as you would not be eligible for the MIS approach.
      </textblock>
